{"id": 889, "genre": 1001, "title": "你无法忍受哪些泪流满面？", "description": "动不动就泪流满面，你先去看看是不是上呼吸道感染吧。（题图来自：HELENA PEREZ GARCIA）", "record_count": 6738, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183709SPJyK0ZcfXj425tz.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-03-26T09:05:45Z", "options": [{"id": 63232, "content": "哭错了情节", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507235}, {"id": 61953, "content": "朝鲜人民。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536656}, {"id": 61700, "content": "演戏流泪，信以为真，曲终人散，还缓不过来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507235}, {"id": 61956, "content": "分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136830}, {"id": 61961, "content": "感动中国人物", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493312}, {"id": 61714, "content": "刻意煽情 編篡故事", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529032}, {"id": 64274, "content": "韩庚回国都多少年了，还在讲自己收到的委屈吧啦吧啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515098}, {"id": 61971, "content": "军训结束教练离开猛哭 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536759}, {"id": 61728, "content": "失恋后", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535046}, {"id": 69153, "content": "看文献，一学习就泪流满面！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575474}, {"id": 61731, "content": "切洋葱?！笑着流泪", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515321}, {"id": 61732, "content": "人类的阴暗面", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535072}, {"id": 61477, "content": "运动员上台领奖，唱国歌的时候，头皮麻麻，眼睛会湿", "image": null, "praise_count": 182, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 266344}, {"id": 61478, "content": "失恋分手对着单身汪哗哗哭还一个劲的各种倾诉 第二天俩人又好了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 608, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465937}, {"id": 61734, "content": "网易云音乐里面，听一首轻音乐，然后一堆人泪流满面，哎，看来全是有故事的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485877}, {"id": 61480, "content": "春晚小品强行结局反转煽情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1122, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 413074}, {"id": 61481, "content": "每一个名人去世，不管认不认识，喜不喜欢，总会泪流面满的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 469, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345973}, {"id": 61993, "content": "苦情戲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536852}, {"id": 61482, "content": "小李子得奥斯卡了，感动，泪流满面！", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345973}, {"id": 66603, "content": "日逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 564267}, {"id": 61483, "content": "丈夫对妻子家暴之后，还吵闹，最后还把自己委屈的泪流满面", "image": null, "praise_count": 260, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416600}, {"id": 61996, "content": "看过一部电视剧（名字忘了）里面的政府官员不贪，老百姓已经感动的泪流满面了（这算高级黑吗？）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536854}, {"id": 61485, "content": "选秀节目煽情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1326, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459807}, {"id": 62765, "content": "所有和我无关的哭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540055}, {"id": 61486, "content": "已经没救的婚姻 硬是要用责任来“感化”一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 160, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253533}, {"id": 61998, "content": "关于关爱父母问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450615}, {"id": 61487, "content": "家里小孩的哭声，噪音简直…还有一些肌肉男的哭哭啼啼，受不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 397835}, {"id": 61743, "content": "xxoo的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535082}, {"id": 61488, "content": "我是歌手的台下观众", "image": null, "praise_count": 904, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479397}, {"id": 61489, "content": "被抛弃的狗狗泪眼看着你                   年迈的环卫工人不论刮风下雨都在认真扫马路                                                           最后，看着亲人或者爱人转身离开的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 524661}, {"id": 62001, "content": "选秀节目各种身世可怜，各种泪流满面", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530157}, {"id": 61490, "content": "你喜欢ta又不敢", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423646}, {"id": 61746, "content": "早上起床眼角莫名有泪，却不知伊人何方。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535094}, {"id": 62002, "content": "选秀节目刚表演完非要讲自己某段惨痛的经历，并强行与自己的梦想联系起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529230}, {"id": 61492, "content": "切洋葱…", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517089}, {"id": 61493, "content": "辣椒进了眼…?", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517089}, {"id": 61749, "content": "莫名其妙的大吼大叫精神分裂泪流满面；综艺节目中说一番我离不开你我们很久不见的伤感之后的垂泪；听个听哭；成年之后遭人欺负委屈的哭；大老爷们嘤嘤嘤嘤的哭…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531386}, {"id": 61494, "content": "看甄嬛痛哭的阿姨们", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 363108}, {"id": 61495, "content": "刻奇Kitsch", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 200506}, {"id": 61751, "content": "大圣归来", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333732}, {"id": 61496, "content": "感觉题目有歧义啊。第一种理解：你对什么事情会控制不住泪流满面？第二种理解：你对哪些泪流满面的情况感到无语。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 520015}, {"id": 61497, "content": "故事伤感，眼泪夺眶而出", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533927}, {"id": 61753, "content": "自己做错事别人都没说啥自己一个人就在哪里哭哭啼啼起来，使得别人不得不过来安慰她，仿佛做错事的是别人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535134}, {"id": 61498, "content": "各类节目主持人赚收视率，不是自己哭就是嘉宾哭", "image": null, "praise_count": 215, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527482}, {"id": 67899, "content": "刻奇", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429045}, {"id": 61499, "content": "想哭就哭呗，怎么就那么矫情╮(╯_╰)╭", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169698}, {"id": 61500, "content": "考上公务员", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533945}, {"id": 61501, "content": "把洋葱都吓哭了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531046}, {"id": 61502, "content": "好朋友因为误会而分手，解除误会和好如初时，泪流满面呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533955}, {"id": 61503, "content": "当伪善将原本值得同情的事烘托为反感", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533956}]}